                    }}
                    >
                    <img style={{height: "50px", width: "50px"}} src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/1995/1995830.png" alt="articulation" />
                    La randonnée libère la respiration
                </div>
            </div>
            <div className='container_ai'>
                <div className='col_ai'
